            These diamonds can be used at your next purchase for a discount. The logic behind that is as follows:
            <table class="table table-hover">
                <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th scope="col">Points</th>
                    <th scope="col">Discount in €</th>
                </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <th scope="row">100</th>
                    <td>4</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th scope="row">200</th>
                    <td>14</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th scope="row">300</th>
                    <td>29</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th scope="row">400</th>
                    <td>48</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th scope="row">500</th>
                    <td>72</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th scope="row">600</th>
                    <td>100</td>
