                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th scope="row">1000</th>
                    <td>251</td>
                </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </p>
    }
    <h2>Cookie policy</h2>
    <p>
        This website will only use necessarry cookies so that the website can function correctly.
    </p>
    <h2>Delivery policy</h2>
    <p>
        As soon as you paid for your product, we will send youre key directly to your e-mail address that you have provided.<br />
        This can take same time. That is why we have 48 hours to send you the key to your address.
    </p>
    <h2>Return policy</h2>
    <p>
        You can not return any products because you can already activate your product key or made a copy of your product key and we cannot sell an used product.<br />
        Once you bought your key(s) you cannot return them.
    </p>
    <h2>Privacy policy</h2>
    <p>
        We will only store personal information that is necessary for our operations and security.<br />
        We will never sell or distribute your personal information.<br />
        We will do everything to secure your personal information.<br />
    </p>
</div>
